title: AHS Apocalypse Episode 10 Review SPOILERS!!
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: They seriously only brought Marie Laveaux back long enough to throw her braids over her shoulder ONE time!😭
My favourite line was myrtle to madison "you grab the gasoline i grab the wood" the delivery was pure comedy gold
Timothy and Emily’s child being the Antichrist was a foreshadowing of the 1st episode when Timothy got out of the shower and saw 666 written on the mirror and a voice said beware
"We modeled her personality after Madison" DEAD. <3
I guess when Venable said "no unauthorized copulation" there was a good reason; those 2 were destined to give birth to the real devil baby!
